title: Cafe Dharma
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, International, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Take-out
description: Fair trade, organic cafe attached to yoga center. Many choices for vegans, but some dishes have egg and cheese. The menu doesn't mark the vegan items, but the staff are knowledgeable. Emphasis on quick light dishes, sandwiches, wraps, and cakes. Relaxed atmosphere with mix of sofas and tables.
